- Use fixtures for setup and teardown to reduce test duplication.
- Implement parameterized tests with `@pytest.mark.parametrize`.
- Use `pytest.raises` to test for expected exceptions.
- Leverage `pytest.mark.asyncio` for testing async functions.
- Use `coverage` to ensure adequate test coverage.